org.apache.ignite.internal.util.typedef.internal

Class CU

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.internal.processors.cache.GridCacheUtils
      • org.apache.ignite.internal.util.typedef.internal.CU

  • public final class CU
extends GridCacheUtils
    Defines internal typedef for GridCacheUtils. Since Java doesn't provide type aliases (like Scala, for example) we resort to these types of measures. This is intended for internal use only and meant to provide for more terse code when readability of code is not compromised.
